      inThisType: 'Si is the ENFP\'s grip function and their least-attended domain. Physical self-care, routine maintenance, and learning from personal history may be chronically underinvested. Under stress, inferior Si erupts as obsessive attention to personal health or symptoms, nostalgic fixation on the past, or anxiety about sensory details that would normally be ignored.',
