      title: 'Extraverted Feeling (Dominant)',
      inThisType: 'For the ENFJ, Fe is the lens through which all experience is filtered. They are perpetually tuned to the emotional climate of their environment, instinctively responding to what the group needs, what individuals need, and how to facilitate connection. Unlike the ESFJ whose Fe is grounded in Si tradition and concrete experience, the ENFJ\'s Fe is guided by Ni toward long-range relational and social vision.',
