      inThisType: 'Ni gives the ENFJ their visionary quality — not just responsiveness to the present emotional climate, but a long-range sense of where people and situations are going. It allows them to see others\' potential with unusual clarity and to perceive the deep patterns behind surface-level interactions. ENFJ Ni provides the strategic underpinning for their social leadership.',
